Class Recipe

java.lang.Object
no.ntnu.idatt1005.foodi.model.objects.dtos.Recipe
Direct Known Subclasses:
RecipeWithIngredients, RecipeWithPartiallyRemovedIngredients
public class Recipe extends Object
This class represents a recipe. A recipe has a name, description, difficulty, and duration. The duration is in minutes.

0.4.0
